  %body
    %header
      .container
        .stage
          %img{:alt => "Richard working", :src => "images/screen-seven-1.png", :class => "screen-img", :id => "img-1", :width => "1200px"}
          %img{:alt => "Richard working", :src => "images/screen-seven-2.png", :class => "screen-img hidden", :id => "img-1", :width => "1200px"}

          %p.dialog#d1 You make your way back to the incubator and you start to feel like you need to make a decision.
          %p.dialog#d2.hidden Your two options are take the 10 million from Gavin Bellson and live out the rest of your days as a millionaire or go with Peter Gregory and get 200 hundred thousand and build the company the way you want it.
          %button{:type => "button",:class => "next-btn hidden", :id => "gavin"}
          %button{:type => "button",:class => "next-btn hidden", :id => "peter"}

          %button{:type => "button",:class => "next-btn", :id => "next-btn-7"}
